svg\" alt=\"\">      <img draggable=\"false\" role=\"img\" class=\"emoji\" src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/svg/1f449.svg\" alt=\"\">       <img draggable=\"false\" role=\"img\" class=\"emoji\" src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/svg/1f449.svg\" alt=\"\">    <img draggable=\"false\" role=\"img\" class=\"emoji\" src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/svg/1f449.svg\" alt=\"\">     <img draggable=\"false\" role=\"img\" class=\"emoji\" src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/svg/1f449.svg\" alt=\"\">     <img draggable=\"false\" role=\"img\" class=\"emoji\" src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/svg/25aa.svg\" alt=\"\">        Contact details: 9807275807,9863448821,9819279502 <img draggable=\"false\" role=\"img\" class=\"emoji\" src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/svg/2714.svg\" alt=\"\">Best quality service provided at most affordable rate all over Nepal. <img draggable=\"false\" role=\"img\" class=\"emoji\" src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/svg/2705.svg\" alt=\"\">Synergy Engineering consultant <img draggable=\"false\" role=\"img\" class=\"emoji\" src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/svg/2705.svg\" alt=\"\">Synergy Construction Company <img draggable=\"false\" role=\"img\" class=\"emoji\" src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/svg/1f6a7.svg\" alt=\"\"> -    <img draggable=\"false\" role=\"img\" class=\"emoji\" src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/svg/1f917.svg\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\";}i:10;a:1:{s:7:\"content\";s:888:\"<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Synergy Engineering Consultant &amp; Construction is a leading construction company specializing in municipality drawing, Autocad 2D &amp; 3D, supervision, estimation, valuation, and structure analysis. Our team of experienced and skilled architects, engineers, and contractors work together to provide high-quality construction services. We offer our clients a one-stop solution for all their construction needs, from design to final handover. Our approach to construction is characterized by transparency, professionalism, and commitment to customer satisfaction. We use the latest technology and construction methods to ensure the safety and efficiency of each project. With competitive pricing and a focus on customer service, Synergy Engineering Consultant &amp; Construction is the right choice for your next construction project.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\";}i:11;a:1:{s:7:\"content\";s:804:\"<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Municipality drawing</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Autocad 2D &amp; 3D</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Supervision</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Estimation</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Valuation</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Structure analysis</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Construction and build management</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Commercial and residential construction</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Consultation and advice</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Contractual services</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\";}i:13;a:1:{s:7:\"content\";s:123:\"<!-- wp:heading {\"textColor\":\"white\"} -->\n<h2 class=\"has-white-color has-text-color\">Our Location</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\";}i:14;a:1:{s:7:\"content\";s:18:\"<!-- wp:embed /-->\";}i:15;a:1:{s:7:\"content\";s:453:\"<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3554.551215023498!2d84.87475591452282!3d27.012742862280717!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x399355096c5e2d1b%3A0x52b6d21c67e4827d!2sSynergy%20Engineering%20consultant%20%26%20construction!5e0!3m2!1sen!2snp!4v1675588019413!5m2!1sen!2snp\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\"></iframe>\";}i:16;a:1:{s:7:\"content\";s:888:\"<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Synergy Engineering Consultant &amp; Construction is a leading construction company specializing in municipality drawing, Autocad 2D &amp; 3D, supervision, estimation, valuation, and structure analysis. Our team of experienced and skilled architects, engineers, and contractors work together to provide high-quality construction services. We offer our clients a one-stop solution for all their construction needs, from design to final handover. Our approach to construction is characterized by transparency, professionalism, and commitment to customer satisfaction. We use the latest technology and construction methods to ensure the safety and efficiency of each project. With competitive pricing and a focus on customer service, Synergy Engineering Consultant &amp; Construction is the right choice for your next construction project.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\";}}', 'yes'),
