vice to clients, and use construction materials that are resistant to natural disasters such as earthquakes. If interested, you can contact them at the given phone numbers. They aim to turn their clients\' dreams into reality by providing the best quality service at an affordable rate.<\\/strong><\\/p>\",\"text_color\":\"#1A0303\",\"_margin\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"22\",\"right\":\"0\",\"bottom\":\"0\",\"left\":\"0\",\"isLinked\":false},\"_background_background\":\"classic\",\"_background_color\":\"#6EC1E405\",\"__globals__\":{\"_background_color\":\"\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"1cd8efa\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":50,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"682273b\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/Synergy%20Construction\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2023\\/02\\/aboutimg.jpg\",\"id\":38,\"alt\":\"\",\"source\":\"library\"},\"title_text\":\"\",\"description_text\":\"\",\"image_space\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":24,\"sizes\":[]},\"image_size\":{\"unit\":\"%\",\"size\":100,\"sizes\":[]}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image-box\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"edd1659\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"margin\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"31\",\"right\":0,\"bottom\":\"0\",\"left\":0,\"isLinked\":false}},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"1bdf079\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"e820adb\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"title\":\"<h3 style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 35px 0px 25px; outline: none; font-family: Montserrat; line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(33, 40, 46); font-size: 40px; letter-spacing: 1px; transition-duration: 1s; text-align: center; text-transform: uppercase; white-space: normal; font-weight: 700 !important;\\\">WHAT WE DO<\\/h3>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"heading\