"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"e873332\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"layout\":\"full_width\",\"stretch_section\":\"section-stretched\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"d0e325a\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"67d0f68\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"tabs\":[{\"tab_title\":\"Construction\",\"tab_content\":\"<p><img class=\\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-29\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/Synergy%20Construction\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2023\\/02\\/Most-Beautiful-House-in-the-World.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"1689\\\" height=\\\"994\\\" \\/><\\/p><p>Our company is dedicated to providing the best quality construction services to our clients all over Nepal. Our team of experienced and skilled architects, engineers, and contractors have extensive knowledge in the field of construction and are capable of handling projects of various sizes and complexities.<\\/p>\",\"_id\":\"268f475\"},{\"tab_title\":\"Consultant\",\"tab_content\":\"<p><img class=\\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-46\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/Synergy%20Construction\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2023\\/02\\/slider04-2.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"1700\\\" height=\\\"1159\\\" \\/><\\/p><p>These services can help ensure that the project is completed on time, within budget, and to the desired quality standards. The scope and extent of a construction company\'s consulting services can vary depending on the company\'s size and expertise. Some companies may specialize in certain types of projects or building methods, while others may offer a more comprehensive range of services.<\\/p>\",\"_id\":\"f37df56\"},{\"_id\":\"acfb6b7\",\"tab_title\":\"Building desgin\",\"tab_content\":\"<p>\\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0\\u00a0<img class=\\\"size-full wp-image-48 aligncenter\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/Synergy%20Construction\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2023\\/02\\/maxresdefault.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"1280\\\" height=\\\"720\\\" \\/><\\/p><p>Building design refers to the broadly based architectural, engineering and technical applications to the design of buildings. All building projects require the services of a building designer, typically a licensed architect. Smaller, less complicated projects often do not require a licensed professional, and the design of such projects is often undertaken by building designers, draftspersons, interior designers (for interior fit-outs or renovations), or contractors.<\\/p>\"},{\"_id\":\"0dc7ab4\",\"tab_title\":\"Map construction\",\"tab_content\":\"<p>\\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0\\u00a0<img class=\\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-49\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/Synergy%20Construction\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2023\\/02\\/Tufts-Logistics-Map.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"1068\\\" height=\\\"630\\\" \\/><\\/p><p><strong>Construction Map<\\/strong>\\u00a0allows you to search and view details of\\u00a0<strong>construction<\\/strong>\\u00a0sites, organisations, suppliers and partners registered with the Considerate Constructors Scheme. The Considerate Constructors Scheme is a not-for-profit, independent organisation founded to raise standards in the\\u00a0<strong>construction<\\/strong>\\u00a0industry\\u00a0<\\/p>\"}],\"tabs_align_horizontal\":\"center\",\"border_width\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":7,\"sizes\":[]},\"background_color\":\"#F4BBBB00\",\"tab_active_color\":\"#E80E28F7\",\"content_color\":\"#0D0202\",\"content_typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"content_typography_font_family\":\"Roboto\",\"content_typography_font_size\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":31,\"sizes\":[]},\"content_typography_font_weight\":\"400\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"tabs\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"0bbfdcb\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"layout\"