s\\/2023\\/02\\/Tufts-Logistics-Map.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"1068\\\" height=\\\"630\\\" \\/><\\/p><p><strong>Construction Map<\\/strong>\\u00a0allows you to search and view details of\\u00a0<strong>construction<\\/strong>\\u00a0sites, organisations, suppliers and partners registered with the Considerate Constructors Scheme. The Considerate Constructors Scheme is a not-for-profit, independent organisation founded to raise standards in the\\u00a0<strong>construction<\\/strong>\\u00a0industry\\u00a0<\\/p>\"}],\"tabs_align_horizontal\":\"center\",\"border_width\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":7,\"sizes\":[]},\"background_color\":\"#F4BBBB00\",\"tab_active_color\":\"#E80E28F7\",\"content_color\":\"#0D0202\",\"content_typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"content_typography_font_family\":\"Roboto\",\"content_typography_font_size\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":31,\"sizes\":[]},\"content_typography_font_weight\":\"400\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"tabs\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"f9659d1\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"b5c10d6\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"d660228\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"spacer\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"0bbfdcb\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"layout\":\"full_width\",\"stretch_section\":\"section-stretched\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"d9f9c83\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"cd48fd9\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"title\":\"Our Works\",\"align\":\"center\",\"title_color\":\"#031720\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"heading\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"afbc4c9\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"layout\":\"full_width\",\"stretch_section\":\"section-stretched\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"86de6a3\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\