n			<h2>Office Design</h2>		\n															<img width=\"525\" height=\"310\" src=\"http://localhost/Synergy%20Construction/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/Tufts-Logistics-Map.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />															\n			<h2>Map Works</h2>		\n															<img width=\"525\" height=\"236\" src=\"http://localhost/Synergy%20Construction/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/309985739_496828465787261_1496622755802263287_n.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />															\n			<h2>Home Construction</h2>		\n															<img width=\"525\" height=\"295\" src=\"http://localhost/Synergy%20Construction/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/326074680_696562235357969_7201985159736498289_n.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />															\n			<h2>Home Design</h2>		\n															<img width=\"525\" height=\"295\" src=\"http://localhost/Synergy%20Construction/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/home.1.949595.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />															\n			<h2>House renovation</h2>		\n			<h2>Get message from us ?</h2>		\n		[fluentform id=\"1\"]		\n			<h2>Our Partners</h2>		\n			<style>/*! elementor - v3.10.2 - 29-01-2023 */\n.elementor-widget-image-carousel .swiper-container{position:static}.elementor-widget-image-carousel .swiper-container .swiper-slide figure{line-height:inherit}.elementor-widget-image-carousel .swiper-slide{text-align:center}.elementor-image-carousel-wrapper:not(.swiper-container-initialized) .swiper-slide{max-width:calc(100% / var(--e-image-carousel-slides-to-show, 3))}</style>		\n								<figure><img src=\"http://localhost/Synergy%20Construction/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/sponsor1-1.png\" alt=\"sponsor1 (1)\" /></figure><figure><img src=\"http://localhost/Synergy%20Construction/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/sponsor5.png\" alt=\"sponsor5\" /></figure><figure><img src=\"http://localhost/Synergy%20Construction/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/sponsor4.png\" alt=\"sponsor4\" /></figure><figure><img src=\"http://localhost/Synergy%20Construction/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/sponsor2.png\" alt=\"sponsor2\" /></figure>			\n												Previous\n												Next\n			<h2>What Our Client Tell About US </h2>		\n								<figure><img src=\"http://localhost/Synergy%20Construction/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/2.png\" alt=\"2\" /></figure><figure><img src=\"http://localhost/Synergy%20Construction/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/3.png\" alt=\"3\" /></figure><figure><img src=\"http://localhost/Synergy%20Construction/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/4.png\" alt=\"4\" /></figure><figure><img src=\"http://localhost/Synergy%20Construction/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/1.png\" alt=\"1\" /></figure>			\n												Previous\n												Next', 'Home', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'home', '', '', '2023-02-05 10:30:11', '2023-02-05 10:30:11', '', 0, 'http://localhost/Synergy%20Construction/?page_id=7', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(8, 1, '2023-02-05 06:48:43', '2023-02-05 06:48:43', '<style>/*! elementor - v3.10.2 - 29-01-2023 */\n.elementor-widget-image{text-align:center}.elementor-widget-image a{display:inline-block}.elementor-widget-image a img[src$=\".svg\"]{width:48px}.elementor-widget-image img{vertical-align:middle;display:inline-block}</style>												<img width=\"525\" height=\"137\" src=\"http://localhost/Synergy%20Construction/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/construction_cover_letter_example_zety_us_1.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />															\n			<style>/*! elementor - v3.10.2 - 29-01-2023 */\n.elementor-heading-title{padding:0;margin:0;line-height:1}.elementor-widget-heading .elementor-heading-title[class*=elementor-size-]>a{color:inherit;font-size:inherit;line-height:inherit}.elementor-widget-heading .elementor-heading-title.elementor-size-small{font-size:15px}.elementor-widget-heading .elementor-heading-title.elementor-size-medium{font-size:19px}.elementor-widget-heading .elementor-heading-title.elementor-size-large{font-size:29px}.elementor-widget-heading .elementor-heading-title.elementor-size-xl{font-size:39px}.elementor-widget-heading .elementor-heading-title.elementor-size-xxl{font-size:59px}</style><h2>Introduction</h2>		\n		<p>Welcome to Synergy Engineering Consultant &amp; Construction, a leading company in the field of construction and engineering services in Nepal. We specialize in providing a full range of services, including municipality drawing, AutoCAD 2D &amp; 3D, supervision, estimation, valuation, and structure analysis. Our team of experienced and skilled architects, engineers, and construction professionals work together to deliver high-quality projects that exceed client expectations.At Synergy Engineering Consultant &amp; Construction, we are dedicated to providing top-notch construction services to our clients. Our team of experienced architects, engineers, and contractors work together to bring your vision to life.</p>		\n			<h2>Expertise</h2>		\n		<p>Our team of experts has years of experience in the construction industry and has the knowledge and skills to handle any project, big or small. We use the latest technologies and techniques to ensure that each project is completed efficiently and effectively. Our team is dedicated to providing the best quality service at an affordable rate to our clients.</p>		\n															<img width=\"525\" height=\"295\" src=\"http://localhost/Synergy%20Construction/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/maxresdefault.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />															\n			<h2>Supervision\n</h2>		\n		<p>At Synergy Engineering Consultant &amp; Construction, we believe in direct supervision to ensure that each project is completed to the highest standard. Our supervisors are on-site at all times to monitor progress and ensure that all work is carried out according to plans and specifications. This direct supervision helps to minimize any potential problems and ensures that each project is completed on time and within budget.</p>		\n															<img width=\"525\" height=\"350\" src=\"http://localhost/Synergy%20Construction/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/iStock-546438774.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />															\n			<h2>Prevention of Damage\n</h2>		\n		<p>We understand that construction projects can often result in damage to the surrounding environment and community. That\'s why we take a proactive approach to minimize any potential damage and ensure that each project is completed with care and sensitivity. Our team takes all necessary measures to protect the environment and surrounding community, including implementing protective measures and taking measures to prevent soil erosion.</p>		\n															<img width=\"525\" height=\"525\" src=\"http://localhost/Synergy%20Construction/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/new-construction-home.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />															\n			<h2>Consultant</h2>		\n		<p>At Synergy Engineering Consultant &amp; Construction, we believe in providing the best quality service to our clients. That\'s why we offer free consultation services to help clients understand the various aspects of their project. Our team of experts is available to provide expert advice and guidance on all aspects of construction, from design and planning to execution and completion.</p>		\n															<img width=\"525\" height=\"358\" src=\"http://localhost/Synergy%20Construction/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/slider04-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />															\n			<h2>Complete Solution</h2>		\n		<p>We offer a complete solution for all construction projects, including the supply of all necessary materials and equipment. Our team works closely with clients to ensure that their vision is realized and that each project is completed to the highest standard. We take a hands-on approach to each project and are dedicated to ensuring that each client is completely satisfied with the final result.</p>		\n															<img width=\"525\" height=\"295\" src=\"http://localhost/Synergy%20Construction/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/home.1.949595.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />															\n			<h2>Commercial and Residential:\n</h2>		\n		<p>At Synergy Engineering Consultant &amp; Construction, we offer our services for both commercial and residential projects. Our team has extensive experience in designing and constructing buildings of all sizes and types, from small homes to large commercial developments. No matter the size or scope of your project, we have the expertise to deliver a high-quality solution that exceeds your expectations.</p>		\n															<img width=\"525\" height=\"295\" src=\"http://localhost/Synergy%20Construction/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/326074680_696562235357969_7201985159736498289_n.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />', 'About Us', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'about-us', '', '', '2023-02-05 10:10:26', '2023-02-05 10:10:26', '', 0, 'http://localhost/Synergy%20Construction/?page_id=8', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(9, 1, '2023-02-05 06:48:43', '2023-02-05 06:48:43', '<style>/*! elementor - v3.10.2 - 29-01-2023 */\n.elementor-widget-image{text-align:center}.elementor-widget-image a{display:inline-block}.elementor-widget-image a img[src$=\".svg\"]{width:48px}.elementor-widget-image img{vertical-align:middle;display:inline-block}</style>												<img width=\"525\" height=\"257\" src=\"http://localhost/Synergy%20Construction/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/types-of-construction-insurance-cover_va5mhk.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />															\n			<style>/*! elementor - v3.10.2 - 29-01-2023 */\n.elementor-heading-title{padding:0;margin:0;line-height:1}.elementor-widget-heading .elementor-heading-title[class*=elementor-size-]>a{color:inherit;font-size:inherit;line-height:inherit}.elementor-widget-heading .elementor-heading-title.elementor-size-small{font-size:15px}.elementor-widget-heading .elementor-heading-title.elementor-size-medium{font-size:19px}.elementor-widget-heading .elementor-heading-title.elementor-size-large{font-size:29px}.elementor-widget-heading .elementor-heading-title.elementor-size-xl{font-size:39px}.elementor-widget-heading .elementor-heading-title.elementor-size-xxl{font-size:59px}</style><h2>OUR SERVICES</h2>		\n			<h2>Commercial and residential construction</h2>		\n															<img width=\"525\" height=\"309\" src=\"http://localhost/Synergy%20Construction/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/Most-Beautiful-House-in-the-World.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />															\n		<p>The company provides construction services for both commercial and residential properties, including new builds, renovations, and remodeling projects.</p>		\n			<h2>Construction and build management</h2>		\n															<img width=\"525\" height=\"299\" src=\"http://localhost/Synergy%20Construction/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/307079235_484363620367079_6368009500644025414_n.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />															\n		<p>We provide design services, including architectural and engineering services, to help clients create a vision for their building project.</p>		\n			<h2>Design</h2>		\n															<img width=\"525\" height=\"295\" src=\"http://localhost/Synergy%20Construction/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/maxresdefault-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />															\n		<p>Construction companies may provide design services, including architectural and engineering services, to help clients create a vision for their building project.</p>		\n			<h2>Construction</h2>		\n															<img width=\"525\" height=\"236\" src=\"http://localhost/Synergy%20Construction/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/309985739_496828465787261_1496622755802263287_n.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />															\n		<p>This is the physical act of building the structure, including laying the foundation, constructing the walls, installing electrical and plumbing systems, and applying finishes such as paint and flooring.</p>		\n			<h2>Autocad 2D & 3D</h2>		\n															<img width=\"525\" height=\"284\" src=\"http://localhost/Synergy%20Construction/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/autocad.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />															\n		<p>Synergy Engineering Consultant &amp; Construction offers drafting services for both 2D and 3D drawings using the latest Autocad software. This includes floor plans, elevations, and detailed drawings for construction.</p>		\n			<h2>Supervision</h2>		\n															<img width=\"525\" height=\"358\" src=\"http://localhost/Synergy%20Construction/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/slider04-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />															\n		<p>The company provides on-site supervision services to ensure that all construction work is completed according to the plans and specifications. This includes monitoring the quality of work, ensuring safety standards are met, and addressing any issues that arise during construction.</p>		\n			<h2>Estimation</h2>		\n															<img width=\"525\" height=\"263\" src=\"http://localhost/Synergy%20Construction/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/construction-estimate.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />															\n		<p>Synergy Engineering Consultant &amp; Construction provides professional cost estimation services to help clients understand the costs involved in their construction project. This includes a detailed breakdown of materials, labor, and other expenses associated with construction.</p>		\n			<h2>Valuation</h2>		\n															<img width=\"290\" height=\"174\" src=\"http://localhost/Synergy%20Construction/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/images.jpeg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />															\n		<p>The company provides professional property valuation services to help clients determine the value of their property for insurance, taxation, or mortgage purposes.</p>		\n			<h2>Structure analysis</h2>		\n															<img width=\"525\" height=\"275\" src=\"http://localhost/Synergy%20Construction/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/structural_design_and_analysis_0.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />															\n		<p>Synergy Engineering Consultant &amp; Construction provides structural analysis services to evaluate the safety and stability of buildings and other structures. This includes evaluating the existing structure, identifying any potential weaknesses, and making recommendations for necessary repairs or improvements.</p>		\n			<h2>Consultation and advice</h2>		\n															<img width=\"525\" height=\"350\" src=\"http://localhost/Synergy%20Construction/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/Is-Consulting-About-Giving-Advice.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />															\n		<p>synergy Engineering Consultant &amp; Construction provides professional consultation and advice to clients to help them make informed decisions about their construction projects. This includes advising on materials, design, and construction methods, as well as identifying any potential risks and limitations.</p>		\n			<h2>Contractual services</h2>		\n															<img width=\"525\" height=\"223\" src=\"http://localhost/Synergy%20Construction/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/No-Room-for-Discretion-in-Contractual-Matters.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />															\n		<p>The company provides contractual services, including contract management, dispute resolution, and project documentation. This helps ensure that all parties involved in the construction project understand their responsibilities and obligations.</p>		\n			<h2>Material sourcing and procurement</h2>		\n															<img width=\"525\" height=\"295\" src=\"http://localhost/Synergy%20Construction/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/1619104099.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />															\n		<p>Synergy Engineering Consultant &amp; Construction provides material sourcing and procurement services to ensure that the right materials are procured at the right price and delivered to the construction site on time.</p>		\n			<h2>Municipality drawing</h2>		\n															<img width=\"525\" height=\"348\" src=\"http://localhost/Synergy%20Construction/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/Residential-Building-Submission-Drawing-30x40-DWG-Free-Download-Model.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />															\n		<p>Synergy Engineering Consultant &amp; Construction provides expert services for municipality drawings, including site plan preparation, architectural drawings, and construction drawings.</p>', 'Our Services', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'our-services', '', '', '2023-02-05 09:47:36', '2023-02-05 09:47:36', '', 0, 'http://localhost/Synergy%20Construction/?page_id=9', 0, 'page', '', 0),
